<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.10.4">
<l>pēca niṉṟa civaṉuk kumpira maṉṟaṉak kumpiṟarkku</l>
<l>nāya kaṉava ṉēka pālanaṉ mōkkattuk kaṇṭukoḷmiṉ</l>
<l>ṟēca māmatiḷ cūḻntaḻa kāya tirukkuru kūrataṉu</l>
<l>ḷīcaṉ pālō ravampa ṟaitaleṉ ṉāvati liṅkiyarkkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He alone is the leader of Śiva, Brahmā and the others who are there</l>
<l>while you speak [of them]. See for yourself the good deliverance from the skull [bowl].</l>
<l>Talking an evil about the lord in Tirukkurukūr that is beautiful, being surrounded by</l>
<l>radiant big walls, what will it be for those [who worship] the linga?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
